<p><strong> 1.录取通知书发放时间 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200820/ee78d94ba8004485822f06211ccf9a80.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
